0.content: Lappland was once part of the influential, bloodthirsty Saluzzoes family. The Saluzzoes family annihiliated Texas's family years ago, with Lappland leading the way. Now that this is in the past, Lappland recoils at the sound of her own family name, due to the fact that she was banished by her father from the Saluzzoes family, and labelled her a "lone wolf", or a Lupine outcast.
